  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/924870/extras/562b0490824c04d1b8696d7129be9207.apng?t=1548946823\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/924870/extras/562b0490824c04d1b8696d7129be9207.poster.avif?t=1548946823\" class=\"bb_img\" width=585 height=135 /></picture></span><br><br><strong>WARP-TEK</strong> is a horizontal space shooter wherein you have to <strong>rescue your pet</strong> after it got abducted by aliens and consequently imprisoned on a distant planet. <br><br>In this game, you will find: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Over <i>20</i> boss types!</strong><br></li><li> <strong><i>30+</i> enemy types!</strong><br></li><li> <strong>A hell of a lot of colours</strong><br></li><li> <strong>More than <i>25</i> weapons to collect and play with!</strong><br></li><li> <strong>References to other indie games!(<i>Squirm</i>, <i>The Misadventures of Melon</i>)</strong><br></li><li> <strong>A warm feeling of satisfaction knowing that you're supporting a happy lil' indie boy!</strong></li></ul>",
